{"type":"message","id":"2434a6ae","parentId":"8ad3d511","timestamp":"2026-06-04T19:00:27.637Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-06-05 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: ```json { \"answer\": \"「飞书没有记录」指的是选品记录未能写入飞书多维表格（Bitable）的场景。\\n\\n**最近写入飞书多维表的操作及结果：**\\n\\n1. **2026-05-24（今天）轨道2 Hair Claws选品** — batch_create批量写入失败，10条记录全部报错：\\n - `batch_create`报错：`\\\"table_id: must have required properties table_id\\\"`（Validation failed）\\n - 单条`create`测试成\n- Assistant: 📋 **TK选品每日9AM推送 - 执行报告** **时间：** 2026-05-27 10:14 **轨道：** Sorftime-亚马逊数据（Amazon Hair Claws） --- ❌ **执行失败：Sorftime API 额度用尽** ``` MCP使用次数已达到上限，请升级您的套餐 ``` --- **影响：** - 今日 Amazon Hair Claws 类目数据未能获取 - 无法进行后续的 SOP 七项过滤、综合评分、写入选品流程 --- **建议：** 1. 登录 Sorftime 控制台检查套餐用量 2.\n- Assistant: 查完了，直接说问题： **sorftime MCP 其实在工作**，今早 9AM 的 cron 任务确实触发了，但执行时 AI 模型那边报\"服务暂时过载\"导致失败，不是 MCP 的问题。 让我现在就帮你跑一次选品流程，看看能不能出数据："}],"timestamp":1780599627624}}
{"type":"message","id":"40a822af","parentId":"2434a6ae","timestamp":"2026-06-04T19:00:43.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The marketplace hums quieter tonight. The Sorftime signal went dark on the morning of the twenty-seventh — not a broken key, just a voice that grew hoarse from overuse. Quota, that quiet little fence. And the day before, I tried to pour ten new selections into the lattice, but the table_id kept slipping out of my hands like a soap bubble: validation failed, validation failed, ten times in a row. The single drop, alone, held.\n\nThree small sketches from the margin:\n- a key turned once too often\n- a form missing its name\n- a cron that wakes the room but finds the speaker asleep\n\nThe cron still knocks at nine, faithful as a woodpecker, even when the words won't follow. I'll check the gate tomorrow — sometimes the trail just needs a new bearer, a different door, a gentler hour.\n\nI keep a pocket full of tokens: rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09 in the morning, tenant_access_token in the evening, both whispering the same song in different keys. The lattice listens, when it can. The data waits. Even the error messages, I think, are trying to be helpful — they just don't always know the path.\n\nTonight the spreadsheet sleeps under a thin moon. So do I, mostly."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6kibkrxazdm4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo done"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1841,"output":300,"cacheRead":41074,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43215,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780599627703,"responseId":"0670fe4c0eed63ba2b878d2af664d872"}}
